CustomFunction.Calculation:
// #P_Required ( name )
// version 1.0, Daniel A. Shockley

/*
	Used to run a normal #P, but also puts that key into a local variable, $paramKeysRequiredList, which indicates that the param is REQUIRED. 


HISTORY:
	1.0 - 2019-06-25 ( dshockley ): First created. 
*/


Let ( [ 
		$paramKeysRequiredList = List ( $paramKeysRequiredList ; name )
	]; 
	#P ( name )
)
